  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个图书馆管理系统的ER图。核心实体有三个：图书馆、图书和用户。图书馆可以包含多本图书，用户需要能访问图书馆，还要有自己的购物车功能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LIBRARY",
        "BOOK",
        "USER",
        "CART"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下关系：图书馆和图书是一对多，这个没问题。用户和图书馆的访问关系是多对多吗？比如一个用户可以访问多个图书馆，一个图书馆也有多个用户？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LIBRARY",
        "BOOK",
        "USER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用户和图书馆是多对多。另外购物车这块，每个用户有且只有一个购物车，购物车可以装多本图书，但一本图书也可能被多个购物车包含。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "CART",
        "BOOK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主体框架画出来。LIBRARY实体有id、name和metadata字段；BOOK实体包含id、libraryId、serialnumber、title、author、description，还有category和onlineStatus两个枚举类型，以及reserved布尔值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LIBRARY",
        "BOOK",
        "ennum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，onlineStatus的命名我确认一下，用驼峰命名onlineStatus可以吗？还有CART实体里的books字段，类型应该是关联到BOOK的集合，不是单个Book。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BOOK",
        "CART",
        "onlineStatus"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下。CART的books字段类型标注为关联BOOK的集合关系，同时确认onlineStatus使用驼峰命名。USER实体我补充了id、username、password、email字段，CART有id、userId。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CART",
        "USER",
        "onlineStatus"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查一下关系：LIBRARY通过contains关联BOOK，USER通过accesses关联LIBRARY，USER通过has关联CART，CART通过contains关联BOOK。这些命名都准确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LIBRARY",
        "BOOK",
        "USER",
        "CART",
        "contains",
        "accesses",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。LIBRARY到BOOK是一对多contains，USER到LIBRARY是多对多accesses，USER到CART是一对一has，CART到BOOK是多对多contains。所有基数和关系名都对应上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LIBRARY",
        "BOOK",
        "USER",
        "CART",
        "contains",
        "accesses",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
